Package de.interactive_instruments.etf.client

Interface TestStepResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TestResult>, TestResult, TestResultMessageHolder
    public interface TestStepResult
extends TestResultMessageHolder, TestResult
    A Test Step is the parent result element of zero or multiple TestAssertionResults and the child of exactly one TestCaseResult. Please note: If the label of this element is set to the value "IGNORE", it will be ignored during the traversal of TestResults.
    See Also:
